8. Reproducibility Guarantee
Exact figure reproduction is guaranteed provided:
    • numpy version is ≥1.17 (random seed API unchanged since 1.17)
    • matplotlib version is ≥3.3 (FancyBboxPatch pad parameter stable)
    • scipy version is ≥1.4
    • The global seed np.random.seed(23) and local seed np.random.seed(7) in fig4() are not modified
    • The script is run as __main__ (not imported as a module, which would skip the seed calls in the module body)

NOTE  If figures are run individually (e.g. calling fig5() in isolation) without first running fig1()–fig4(), the global seed will be at a different RNG state. Always run the full script via python gen_figures_hires.py for exact paper figures.

